This is the @cite{user documentation} for BashStyle-NG.

Copyright @copyright{} 2007 - 2026 Christopher Roy Bratušek.

BashStyle-NG is a graphical user interface for managing Bash and co. BashStyle-NG
runs on bash startup if enabled to manage all desired settings, aswell as
creating configuration files and providing additionial utilities.

